        <h2>References</h2>
        <p>The following relevant learning materials have been used:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>C# 10 and .NET 6 by Mark J. Price, which can be purchased <a href="https://www.amazon.com/10-NET-Cross-Platform-Development-websites/dp/1801077363">here</a>.</li>
            <li>ASP.NET Core MVC with EF Core - tutorial series by Microsoft, which can be found <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/data/ef-mvc/?view=aspnetcore-6.0">here</a>.</li>
            <li>Quick CRUD app example - ASP.NET Core Crash Corse by Shad Sluiter, which can be found here <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BfEjDD8mWYg&t=2785s">here</a>.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
